{
  "page": "Feature quote/175",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“If you've had the <a href=\"/index.php/Horn_of_Joramun\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Horn of Joramun\">Horn of Joramun</a> all along, why haven't you used it? Why bother building <a href=\"/index.php/Turtle_(siege_engine)\" title=\"Turtle (siege engine)\">turtles</a> and sending <a href=\"/index.php/Thenn_(people)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thenn (people)\">Thenns</a> to kill us in our beds? If this horn is all the songs say, why not just sound it and be done?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a><br />“We <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> know things you kneelers have forgotten. Sometimes the short road is not the safest, Jon Snow. The <a href=\"/index.php/Horned_Lord\" title=\"Horned Lord\">Horned Lord</a> once said that <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">sorcery</a> is a sword without a hilt. There is no safe way to grasp it.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Dalla\" title=\"Dalla\">Dalla</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_73\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 73\">Chapter 73</a>, Jon X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405015610\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 114/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐exp